  "description": "I\u0026rsquo;d like to babble about my babbles, and my babble log (or blog).\nThis is the first text I\u0026rsquo;m writing with GnoponEmacs with the intention and capability of it being published straight to my website.\nAnyway, a babble, as I\u0026rsquo;ve defined it, is one of the least-structured forms of text I\u0026rsquo;ve encoded in my files, and so serves as a good spot for, well, babbling: just kind of writing about whatever comes to mind, as it comes to mind.\n",
